Introduction:

How to use the RHEV API with Javascript using jQuery $.ajax() to handle
REST requests.

This example only works in Firefox by disabling Same-Origin Policy (SOP).
Find more info about SOP limitations and CORS at:

https://fedorahosted.org/pipermail/rhevm-api/2011-January/000658.html

Usage:

- Download the file rhev-api-js-demo.htm
- Open it locally with your browser: firefox rhev-api-js-demo.htm
- Accept the security warning requesting to disable SOP for this page

